    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>利用 GitHub 搭建 blog，减少服务器维护成本。</p><h2 id="github环境步骤："><a href="#github环境步骤：" class="headerlink" title="github环境步骤："></a>github环境步骤：</h2><p>1.创建username.github.io仓库，地址就是这个。username是GitHub的username</p><p>2.随便添加个index.html。URL地址是上面的名字，如果打不开可以在settings找到github pages。点一下就能打开。</p><p>3.用自己的域名解析，需要设置Custom domain。</p><p>gitee环境步骤：</p><h2 id="安装NodeJs需要配置插件仓库。"><a href="#安装NodeJs需要配置插件仓库。" class="headerlink" title="安装NodeJs需要配置插件仓库。"></a>安装NodeJs需要配置插件仓库。</h2><p>因为NodeJs使用国外仓库，下载插件相当慢。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;方法一：安装cnpm插件，配置国内地址相当于私服，用私服cnpm install</span><br><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry&#x3D;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;方法二：设置npm仓库地址 </span><br><span class="line">npm config set registry https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="使用node命令安装hexo框架"><a href="#使用node命令安装hexo框架" class="headerlink" title="使用node命令安装hexo框架"></a>使用node命令安装hexo框架</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>js </span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;安装hexo</span><br><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli </span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;在你的文件夹初始化</span><br><span class="line">hexo init </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;启动 start</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;创建新文章</span><br><span class="line">hexo n</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;清理</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;生成(generate)</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;安装git插件，需要修改_config.yml</span><br><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;上传到git</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>样式</p><p>去github上找，将样式clone 到 \blog\themes，修改_cofing.yml的themes</p><p>维护</p><p>blog文件目录：/source/_posts</p><p>删除文章</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在&#x2F;source&#x2F;_posts删除，hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
